{"type":"text","timestamp":1775894541278,"sessionID":"ses_284741f09ffeSM9AmLfmYyVH1o","part":{"id":"prt_d7b9000cc001vcP9r0WfySPMtZ","messageID":"msg_d7b8fc912001pGE3dx1m1o05Zz","sessionID":"ses_284741f09ffeSM9AmLfmYyVH1o","type":"text","text":"## AR-040 Archive Summary: Python SDK/CLI 测试\n\n### Completed\n\n**T-1 — Fix existing test bugs:** All pre-existing test bugs fixed (method naming, mock response issues, kwargs mismatch). Base 172 tests stabilized.\n\n**T-2 — Extend `test_code_interpreter.py` (635 lines):** Added tests for `CodeInterpreterClient` — `stop()` edge cases (None session_id, missing clients, idempotency), `run_code()` language variants (python3/py/case-insensitive/unsupported), `execute_command()` input handling, `_session_created` flag behavior, data plane init failure cleanup paths.\n\n**T-3 — Extend `test_data_plane.py` (641 lines):** Added tests for `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` — HTTP error propagation, timeout buffer calculations (+2.0s), `write_file` (unicode/empty), `upload_file` (session header/multipart), `download_file` (path stripping/local file creation), `list_files`, `run_code` delegation, default/custom timeout tuples.\n\n**T-4 — Extend `test_control_plane.py` (370 lines):** Added tests for `ControlPlaneClient` — metadata=None, trailing slash URL, default params, `delete_session` (404 idempotent/500/exception), auth token resolution (explicit > SA token > missing > empty), workload manager URL from env/missing.\n\n**T-5 — Extend `test_agent_runtime.py` (837 lines):** Added tests for `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` and `AgentRuntimeClient` — HTTP error propagation, empty payload, per-request session header, timeout tuples, bootstrap/close/idempotency, context manager exception handling, session_id validation.\n\n**T-6 — Extend `test_utils.py` (93 lines):** Added tests for `create_session`, `read_token_from_file`, `get_logger` — edge cases for empty files, whitespace, handler deduplication, formatter verification, string/int levels.\n\n**T-8 — Verification:** 175 tests collected, **175 passed, 0 failures**. Overall coverage **99%** (1 line missing in `code_interpreter.py:122`). All module-level targets met or exceeded.\n\n### Deferred\n\n**T-7 — `test_integration.py` (cross-component integration tests):** Not created. 20 planned integration tests covering full lifecycle flows (CodeInterpreterClient create→execute→stop, AgentRuntimeClient bootstrap→invoke→close, context manager paths, timeout propagation, file operation delegation, env var precedence) were **not implemented**. The unit tests cover individual components thoroughly but lack end-to-end mock-verified integration scenarios.","time":{"start":1775894541275,"end":1775894541275}}}
